org.pistoiaalliance.helm.HELMSimilarityLibrary

Class PathGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pistoiaalliance.helm.HELMSimilarityLibrary.PathGenerator

  • public class PathGenerator
extends Object
    PathGenerator class takes a moleculeGraph and finds all path from each monomer (vertex) up to a maximal length (searchDepth). Paths are found by depth first search.
    Author:
    bueltel
